{"type": "article", "id": 19870, "title": "波浪线条结构的家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-29T07:40:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113536p3IGig2aTYtWwMJE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些带有波浪线条的茶几和书架来自乌克兰的设计师 Max Voytenko，茶几台面用了一块透明玻璃，让人们将注意力放到黑色金属的波浪结构，就像地面上凭空出现几根黑色线条，流畅而跳跃，是简单而带有活力的设计。书架是挂在墙上的，也用波浪做出了立体感，书本可以叠放在架子上，成为墙面的装饰。有黑、蓝、黄三种颜色，<a href=\"http://linestudio.com.ua/gallery-category/objects\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502224saAUBqp27cm5DMj.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150222yHUD98p5fLFjIqgW.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1163\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.24252137\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150223H1VahMTIGycFeqxv.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"755\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80662393\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150223XvWxfLUuFTRd61gE.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"754\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}